## Standards

Read the applicable standards before writing code:

```bash
cat standards/standards.yml       # Index of all standards
cat standards/global/code-style.md
cat standards/global/minimal-changes.md
```

Standards are living documents. The `/learn` skill promotes proven patterns from `.chaos/learnings.md` into `standards/` over time.

